OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mainly dry
OL,6,Fstart to the evening with just the odd
OL,7,Fshower. More persistent rain and
OL,8,Fdrizzle then spreading from the west
OL,9,Fovernight and turning heavy at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FA cloudy day with outbreaks of
OL,12,Frain some of which will be heavy at
OL,13,Ftimes, but there should be a few drier
OL,14,Finterludes too, especially later.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBright
OL,17,Fspells and some heavy showers Tuesday.
OL,18,FDry start Wednesday then some showers.
OL,19,FMostly cloudy with showers on
OL,20,FThursday, and quite breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
